<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
				
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" src="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.file.force.com/file-asset-public/Alliance_Rural_Remote_Email_heade?oid=00DAD00000BK4sL" style="max-width: 683.05px" title="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;">
						<p><b><span style="color:#3498db;">PLEASE CONFIRM YOU HAVE RECEIVED THIS INFORMATION BY REPLYING TO THIS EMAIL.</span></b><br />
						<br />
						Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

						<p>Congratulations on your contract at [Facility Name]. If you could please send us a brief message to let us know once you have arrived on location safely, it would be appreciated. 😊<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						<span style="color:#e67e22;"><b>Please note you are not to contact the facility/accommodation team directly for any accommodation issues, all issues are to be directed to Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health in the first instance.</b></span><br />
						<br />
						Roster and accommodation details for your placement below:</p>
						<strong>Roster:</strong> [Roster details]

						<p>*Please be aware that the roster is only accurate at the time this email was sent. Please ensure you check your roster on arrival to be updated of any amendments to the above.<br />
						<br />
						<strong>Accommodation:</strong>&nbsp;[Accommodation Details]</p>
						<strong>Orientation Checklist</strong> – To be returned within 48hrs of commencing your contract. Click on this link to complete the orientation checklist online:&nbsp;<a href="https://forms.office.com/r/4UNFTtYsZB">https://forms.office.com/r/4UNFTtYsZB</a>

						<p>The Orientation Checklist is not just a tool to assist in orientating you to your new work environment effectively, it also flags for you and us if there are any Occupational Health &amp; Safety issues that we need to address in order to&nbsp;make your work environment safe for you. Please assist us to support you as best we can by returning this form.<br />
						&nbsp;</p>
						<strong>Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health Emergency contact information:</strong>

						<p>Office hours number: <a href="tel:0749985550">07 4998 5550</a> (QLD Time)<br />
						Afterhours Mobile: <a href="tel:0419716809">0419 716 809</a> – This number can be located on your ID Badge.&nbsp;We ask that you only use the Afterhours mobile number for urgent situations that cannot wait until the next business day.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						<strong>Incidents/Statements – IMPORTANT! </strong>If an incident occurs whilst you are on contract, you must&nbsp;notify us of the events that happened as soon as possible.<br />
						<br />
						Under the provisions of our <strong>Professional Indemnity Insurance</strong>, you are only covered if our Insurer is notified that an incident has arisen. Also&nbsp;under the provisions of our Indemnity Insurance, we are required to view any signed statements prior to you providing it to a third party.<br />
						<br />
						<strong>Travelling by Car</strong><br />
						Please keep track of your kilometres travelled from your homebase to the facility (by most direct route) so you can provide this directly to NSW Health as they will be responsible for reimbursement.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						<strong>Buddy Bonus Details</strong><br />
						Simply refer your Nursing friends or Nurses you meet whilst on contract, and when your referral applies with us, ask them to tell us your name. We then pay you a bonus on completion of your buddy’s first contract<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						If you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact us on <a href="tel:0749985550">07 4998 5550</a> &nbsp;or via&nbsp;email.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Travel Safely.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Kind regards,<br />
						{{{Sender.FirstName}}}&nbsp;{{{Sender.LastName}}}<br />
						Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
